about.description: Studying Systems Analysis and Development, my focus is on Front End Development. I have experience with JavaScript and SAP UI5, as well as familiarity with tools and languages such as React, Git / Github, HTML / CSS, Adobe Photoshop, Figma and Bootstrap. I have certifications in Azure Fundamentals, Azure Data Fundamentals and Azure AI Fundamentals from Microsoft, reflecting my commitment to constant evolution and learning. With English skills at the intermediate level, I am ready to face challenges and contribute to innovative projects in the field of Front End Development.
